'''Roger Federer''' d amyurar n waddal n [[Tennis]] tmurt [[Taswist]], ilul ass n {{azmez|8|ɣuct|1981}} di temdint n [[Bâle]].
Yebda yetturar d terbaɛt tameqqṛant aseggas n 1998 , yeḥrez amḍiq amenzu n ubellez n ATP azal n 237 imalas yemseḍfaren (285 ḥalarmi d 6 Yunyu 2010). Ass n 8 Yulyu 2012, yewwi tadwilt n Wimbledon i tikkelt tis sebɛa, yeqḍa-d amyurar [[Pete Sampras]] deg umḍan n tedwilin n Wimbledon i yeḥrez akked imalas i yella di tqacucut n ubellez n ATP (Imalas wis 286).

Yeḥrez ar assa 77 izwilen, gar-asen 23 imeqqṛanen (17 n Grand Chelems d 6 teqbucin n Masters) d 20 n Masters 1000. Yewwi rebɛa n telɣuɣa n Grand Chelem i yellan deg umaḍal, win n Melburn di [[Lusṭrali]], win n RG di lpari tamurt n [[Fṛansa]], win n Wimbledon di tmurt n [[Lengliz]], win Flushing meadows di [[Marikan|Timura Yedduklen n Marikan]].

Deg ubellez n ''Sports Illustrated'' n useggas 2010, Roger Federer yella-d d anadal wis sin yettxelliṣen aṭas n yedrimen deffir [[Tiger Woods]] imi yeṣṣaweḍ ar assa azal n 72 Ifeḍ n dullar deg izwilen yark i yurar.

== Tameddurt ==
[[Tugna:Federer.jpg|thumb|upright|Roǧer Federer di [[Masters n Sinsinati 2005|Masters n Sinsinati]]]]
Ilul Roger Federer ass n {{azmez|8|ɣuct|1981}} di temdint n [[Bâle]], yemma-s, Lynete n [[Tafriqt n Unẓul|tefriqt n wenẓul]], ma d baba-s d aswisit, Robert. Isin yid-sen xedmen di taɣult n [[Tanesfarit|tnesfarit]]. Roger d weltma-s tameqqṛant Diana idiren di temẓi-nsen di [[Münchenstein]] Taswist Talmanit. 
Tura Roger yettidir di [[Wollerau]], tama n [[Schwytz]], netta d tmeṭṭut-is Mirka d yessi-s takniwin Myla Rose d Charlene Riva. Yesɛa tanaslit Taswisit d tin n tefriqt n Unẓul.

Di temẓis Roger Federer yetturar daɣen ddabax uḍar, yella yezweṛ s waṭas, maca d addal n [[Tennis]] i yefren mi yella di Tam (8) iseggasen di lɛemṛis, ɣas akken mazal-it yeṭṭafaṛ ar assa u iḥemmel aṭas tarbaɛt n ddabax uḍar n [[FC Bâle]].

